iane Moscato]]\n|-\n! 13\n| [[Melia Heimbuck]]\n|}\n\n===Pairs===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Name\n|- bgcolor=\"gold\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''1'''\n| [[Kenna Bailey]] / John Denton\n|- bgcolor=\"silver\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''2'''\n| [[Jennifer Heurlin]] / [[John Fredericksen]]\n|- bgcolor=\"cc9966\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''3'''\n| [[Natasha Kuchiki]] / [[Richard Alexander (figure skater)|Richard Alexander]]\n|- bgcolor=\"#d1c571\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''4'''\n| [[Paula Visingardi]] / [[Jeb Rand]]\n|-\n! 5\n| [[Sara Powell]] / [[Robert Powell (figure skater)|Robert Powell]]\n|-\n! 6\n| [[Anne Marie Wells]] / [[Brian Wells (figure skater)|Brian Wells]]\n|-\n! 7\n| [[Catherine Baffo]] / [[John Liotta]]\n|-\n! 8\n| [[Jocelyn Cox]] / [[Brad Cox (figure skater)|Brad Cox]]\n|-\n! 9\n| [[Dawn Piepenbrink]] / [[Tim Dever]]\n|-\n! 10\n| [[Hilary Olney]] / [[Jeffrey Meyers (figure skater)|Jeffrey Meyers]]\n|-\n! 11\n| [[Wendy Weston]] / [[Alexander Enzmann]]\n|-\n! 12\n| [[Dawn Goldstein]] / [[Troy Goldstein]]\n|-\n! 13\n| [[Aimee Offner]] / [[Brian Helgenberg]]\n|-\n! 14\n| [[Tiffany Bailey]] / [[Richard Gillam]]\n|}\n\n===Ice dancing===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Name\n|- bgcolor=\"gold\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''1'''\n| [[Elizabeth Punsalan]] / [[Shawn Rettstatt]]\n|- bgcolor=\"silver\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''2'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=\"cc9966\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''3'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=\"#d1c571\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''4'''\n| \n|-\n! ...\n| \n|-\n! 13\n| [[Julie Benz]] / [[David Schilling]]\n|-\n! ...\n| \n|}\n\n==Novice-level results==\n\n===Men===\nChris Browne 1st \u201cGold medal\u201d\nMichael Chack 2nd\nTom Incantalupo 3rd\n\n==Novice-level results==\n===Men===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Name\n|- bgcolor=\"gold\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''1'''\n| [[ Chris Browne]]\n|- bgcolor=\"silver\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''2'''\n| [[Michael Chack]]\n|- bgcolor=\"cc9966\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''3'''\n| [[Paul Dulebohn]]\n|- bgcol