astic Tree album)|Chandelier]]''\n*\"Ghost\", song by [[Tom Swoon]]\n*\"Ghost\", song by Sir Sly from ''[[Gold (Sir Sly EP)|Gold]]''\n*\"Ghost\", song by [[Skip the Use]] from ''Can Be Late''\n*\"Ghost\", song by Slash from ''[[Slash (album)|Slash]]''\n*\"Ghost\", the first part of the song \"[[Haunted (Beyonc\u00e9 song)|Haunted]]\" recorded by Beyonc\u00e9\n*\"GHOST!\", song by Kid Cudi from ''[[Man on the Moon II: The Legend of Mr. Rager]]''\n*[[Ghosts (Dirty Vegas song)|\"Ghosts\" (Dirty Vegas song)]], 2002\n*[[Ghosts (Japan song)|\"Ghosts\" (Japan song)]], 1982\n*[[Ghosts (Ladytron song)|\"Ghosts\" (Ladytron song)]]\n*[[Ghosts (Laura Marling song)|\"Ghosts\" (Laura Marling song)]], 2007\n*[[Ghosts (Michael Jackson song)|\"Ghosts\" (Michael Jackson song)]]\n*[[Ghosts (Robbie Williams song)|\"Ghosts\" (Robbie Williams song)]]\n*\"Ghosts\", song by 1 Giant Leap from ''[[1 Giant Leap (album)|1 Giant Leap]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by Assemblage 23 from ''[[Meta (Assemblage 23 album)|Meta]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", composition by Albert Ayler from ''[[Spiritual Unity]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by Big Wreck from ''[[Ghosts (Big Wreck album)|Ghosts]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by Ghosts from ''[[The World Is Outside]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by Kansas from ''[[In the Spirit of Things]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by Mike Shinoda from ''[[Post Traumatic]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by Rage from ''[[Ghosts (Rage album)|Ghosts]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by Shellac from ''[[1000 Hurts]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by Susumu Hirasawa from ''[[Berserk (1997 TV series)#Soundtrack|Sword-Wind Chronicle BERSERK Original Soundtrack]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by PVRIS from ''[[White Noise (PVRIS album)|White Noise]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by The Jam from ''[[The Gift (The Jam album)|The Gift]]''\n*\"Ghosts\", song by The Presets from ''[[Pacifica (The Presets album)|Pacifica]]''\n\n====Other music====\n*''Ghost'', [[Piano Trios, Op. 70 (Beethoven)|Piano Trio by Beethoven]]\n*[[Ghost note]], type of musical note\n\n===Other arts, entertainment, and media===\n*''[[Ghost the Musical]]'', 2011 stage musical\n\n===Television===\n====Series====\n*[[Ghosts (1995 TV series)|''Ghosts'' (1995 TV series)]], a BBC series\n*[[Ghost (2008 TV series)|''Ghost'' (2008 TV series)]], Malaysian mystery series\n*[[Ghost (Korean TV series)|''Ghost'' (Korean TV series)]], 2012 police procedural series\n*[[Ghosts (2019 TV series)|''Ghosts'' (2019 TV series)]], a 2019 BBC sitcom\n*''[[Kamen Rider Ghost]]'', a 2015-16 TV Asahi tokusatsu series\n\n====Episodes====\n*\"Ghost\", an [[List of Dollhouse episodes|episode of ''Dollhouse'']]\n*[[Ghosts (Gotham)|\"Ghosts\" (''Gotham'')]]\n*\"Ghosts\", an [[List of Hidden Palms episodes|episode of ''Hidden Palms'']]\n*\"Ghosts\", an [[List of One Day at a Time (2017 TV series) episodes|episode of ''One Day at a Time'']]\n*\"Ghosts\", from [[Psych (season 3)#Episodes|''Psych'' season 3]]\n*\"Ghosts\", an [[List of The Protector episodes|episode of ''The Protector'']]\n*[[The Ghost (Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.)|\"The Ghost\" (''Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.'')]]\n*[[The Ghost (episode)|\"The Ghost\" (episode)]], from ''Miracles''\n\n====Other television====\n*[[Ghosting (television)]], unwanted image\n\n==Computing and technology==\n*[[Ghost (blogging platform)]], blogging software built in JavaScript\n*[[Ghost (disk utility)]], disk cloning program\n*[[Ghost (operating system)]], an operating system project\n*[[G.ho.st]], operating system\n*[[IAI Ghost]], rotary mini UAV\n\n==Science==\n===Biology===\n*[[Ghost cell]], enlarged eosinophilic epithelial cell with eosinophilic cytoplasm but without a nucleus\n*[[Ghost lineage]], an inferred phylogenetic lineage\n*[[Ghost population]], an inferred statistical population\n\n===Physics===\n*[[Ghost (physics)]], unphysical state in quantum field theory\n**[[Faddeev\u2013Popov ghost]]s, extraneous fields introduced into gauge quantum field theories to maintain the consistency of the path integral formulation\n\n==Other uses==\n*[[Ghost (fashion brand)]