z, believing McGuire is a crucial figure in the gang, travels to Glasgow. Another suspect, Callum, commits suicide and, as custody officer, DC Sandy Wilson is under investigation. \n |LineColor       = 96e041\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|Shetland (TV series)\n |EpisodeNumber   = 24\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 4\n |Title           = Episode 4\n |DirectedBy      = Isabelle Sieb\n |WrittenBy       = Paul Logue\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|03|05}}\n |Aux4            = 6.65\n |ShortSummary    = Believing Zezi is still on the island, Perez and the team continue the search for her. Lennox confronts Perez, accusing him of failing her children.\n |LineColor       = 96e041\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|Shetland (TV series)\n |EpisodeNumber   = 25\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 5\n |Title           = Episode 5\n |DirectedBy      = Isabelle Sieb\n |WrittenBy       = David Kane\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|03|12}}\n |Aux4            = 6.66\n |ShortSummary    = Another trafficked victim only known as Niki turns up dead. The pressure for Perez to find Zezi becomes intense, as he believes she is at almost immediate risk. Lennox confronts the only surviving Hayes family member, Jamie.\n |LineColor       = 96e041\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|Shetland (TV series)\n |EpisodeNumber   = 26\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 6\n |Title           = Episode 6\n |DirectedBy      = Isabelle Sieb\n |WrittenBy       = Paul Logue\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|03|19}}\n |Aux4            = 6.80\n |ShortSummary    = The net starts to close in around the expected location of Zezi; despite this, Lennox is suicidal. Duncan Hunter, having discovered more bodies floating in the surf, is traumatised.\n |LineColor       = 96e041\n}}\n|}\n\n==International broadcasts==\n* [[Television in Australia|Australia]]: The programme airs on [[BBC First]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Shetland |website=BBC First |url=http://www.bbcaustralia.com/shows/shetland }}</ref> and [[ABC (Australian TV channel)|ABC]] in Australia. Series 1-3 is also available on Netflix.\n* [[Television in Belgium|Belgium]]: The programme began airing on Flemish public broadcaster [[Vlaamse Radio- en Televisieomroeporganisatie|VRT]]'s main channel, [[\u00e9\u00e9n]], in October 2015.<ref>{{cite web |title=Nieuwe fictie op E\u00e9n: Shetland |trans-title=New fiction on One: Shetland |website=E\u00e9n |language=Dutch |url=http://www.een.be/programmas/een/nieuwe-fictie-op-een-shetland |archive-date=3 March 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303143507/http://www.een.be/programmas/een/nieuwe-fictie-op-een-shetland }}</ref>\n* [[Television in Canada|Canada]]: The series is broadcast on British Columbia's [[Knowledge Network]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Shetland |website=British Columbia's Knowledge Network |publisher=Knowledge Network Corporation|url=https://www.knowledge.ca/program/shetland }}</ref> and streamed on Netflix.<ref>https://www.netflix.com/ca/title/80133848</ref>\n* [[Television in Denmark|Denmark]]: Danish network [[DR 1]] began showing ''Shetland'' in October 2015.<ref>{{cite web |title=Shetland: R\u00f8dt st\u00f8v |trans-title=Shetland: Red dust |website=DR |language=Danish |url=https://www.dr.dk/tv/se/shetland/shetland-roedt-stoev?app_mode=true&platform=undefined,assetType=SpokenSubtitles,assetType=SpokenSubtitles }}</ref>\n* [[Television in Germany|Germany]]: The series began airing on [[Das Erste]] at the end of March 2016.<ref>{{cite web |title=Mord auf Shetland |trans-title=Murder on Shetland |website=fernsehserien.de |publisher=imfernsehen GmbH & Co. KG |language=German |url=http://www.fernsehserien.de/shetland }}</ref>\n* [[Television in Ireland|Ireland]]: The series began airing on Virgin Media in February 2019\n* [[Television in Italy|Italy]]: The series began airing on [[Giallo  (TV channel)|Giallo]] in March 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tvblog.it/post/1519799/elenco-serie-tv-2018-calendario-partenze|title=Elenco Serie Tv 2018: calendario partenze|date=11 December 2017|access-date=12 December 2017|lang=it}}</ref>\n* [[Television in Finland|Finland]]: Viewers in Finland were able to start watching the show from August 2015 on public broadcaster [[YLE]]'s main TV1 channel, where the show was titled \"{{lang|fi|Shetlandsaarten murhat}}.\"<ref>{{cite web |title=Shetlandsaarten murhat |trans-title=Shetland Islands Murder |website=Yle TV1 |language=Finnish |url=http://yle.fi/aihe/artikkeli/2015/08/20/shetlandsaarten-murhat }}</ref>\n* [[Television in the Netherlands|Netherlands]]: ''Shetland'' is aired as part of the \"Detectives\" series from [[KRO-NCRV]] on [[NPO 1]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Detectives |website=NPO |language=Dutch |url=http://www.npo.nl/detectives |archive-date=15 February 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215072553/http://www.npo.nl/detectives }}</ref>\n* [[Television in New Zealand|New Zealand]]: The programme began airing in New Zealand on [[Vibe (TV channel)|Vibe]] in January 2016.<ref>{{cite web |first=Jane |last=Clifton |date=14 January 2016 |title=TV Review: Shetland |website=Stuff |publisher=Fairfax New Zealand Limited |url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/tv-radio/75861491/tv-review-shetland }}</ref>\n* [[Television in Norway|Norway]]: ''Shetland'' is aired on public broadcaster [[NRK]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Shetland |website=NRK TV |language=Norwegian |url=https://tv.nrk.no/serie/shetland }}</ref>\n* [[Television in Spain|Spain]]: The programme began airing in Galicia on [[Televisi\u00f3n de Galicia]] in October 2015.\n* [[Television in Portugal|Portugal]]: The programme began airing in Portugal on [[Fox Crime]] in August 2016.<ref>{{cite web |title=Shetland |website=FOX Portugal |publisher=Fox Networks Group Portugal, Lda |language=Portuguese |url=http://www.foxtv.pt/series/foxcrime/shetland }}</ref>\n* [[Television in Slovenia|Slovenia]]: The programme began airing in Slovenia on public broadcaster [[RTVSLO]] in July 2015.<ref>{{cite web |title=Napovednik |website=MMC RTV Slovenija |language=Slovenian |url=http://www.rtvslo.si/napovednik/shetlandske-skrivnosti-zakopane-skrivnosti-skotska-mini-serija-1-4-ponovitev/153750 }}</ref>\n* [[Television in Sweden|Sweden]]: Swedish public broadcaster [[SVT]] started airing the 3rd series in January 2016 on their primary network SVT1.<ref>{{cite web |title=Shetland |website=SVT |publisher=Sveriges Television AB |language=Swedish |url=http://www.svt.se/shetland/ }}</ref>\n* [[Television in the United States|United States]]: The series is broadcast on many stations of the [[Public Broadcasting System]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Shetland |website=WGBH |url=http://www.wgbh.org/programs/Shetland-3236 }}</ref>\n*The series became available on [[Netflix]] in 2016. In 2018, the [[Britbox]] streaming service acquired the exclusive rights to Shetland\u2019s Series 4, releasing new episodes weekly. Similarly, Series 5 has been released one episode per week beginning April 30, 2019. <ref> {{cite web |title=The wait is finally over. Jimmy Perez is back. | website=Twitter | url=https://twitter.com/britbox_us/status/1123238287785824256?s=21}} </ref> In April 2019, Netflix dropped the series from its streaming service in the USA.  <ref> {{cite web |title=When will Season 4 & 5 of Shetland be on Netflix? | website=WhatsOnNetflix | url=https://www.whats-on-netflix.com/news/when-will-season-4-5-of-shetland-be-on-Netflix/}} </ref> [[Amazon (company)|Amazon]] has Series 1-3 available for fee purchase by episode or by season but is not included in its Prime streaming subscription. (Note that Series 1 [2 episodes] and Series 2 [6 episodes] are essentially bundled into one season for purchase.)\n\n==Accolades==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" \n|- style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Award\n! scope=\"col\"| Category\n! scope=\"col\"| Recipient(s) and nominee(s)\n! scope=\"col\"| Result\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n|20